{"snp3.11:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 3.11 ","snp3.11:0.2":"Nalakasutta ","snp3.11:1.1":"Anandajate tidasagane patite, ","snp3.11:1.2":"Sakkanca indam sucivasane ca deve; ","snp3.11:1.3":"Dussam gahetva atiriva thomayante, ","snp3.11:1.4":"Asito isi addasa divavihare. ","snp3.11:2.1":"Disvana deve muditamane udagge, ","snp3.11:2.2":"Cittim karitvana idamavoca tattha; ","snp3.11:2.3":"“Kim devasangho atiriva kalyarupo, ","snp3.11:2.4":"Dussam gahetva ramayatha kim paticca. ","snp3.11:3.1":"Yadapi asi asurehi sangamo, ","snp3.11:3.2":"Jayo suranam asura parajita; ","snp3.11:3.3":"Tadapi netadiso lomahamsano, ","snp3.11:3.4":"Kimabbhutam datthu maru pamodita. ","snp3.11:4.1":"Selenti gayanti ca vadayanti ca, ","snp3.11:4.2":"Bhujani photenti ca naccayanti ca; ","snp3.11:4.3":"Pucchami voham merumuddhavasine, ","snp3.11:4.4":"Dhunatha me samsayam khippa marisa”. ","snp3.11:5.1":"“So bodhisatto ratanavaro atulyo, ","snp3.11:5.2":"Manussaloke hitasukhatthaya jato; ","snp3.11:5.3":"Sakyana game janapade lumbineyye, ","snp3.11:5.4":"Tenamha tuttha atiriva kalyarupa. ","snp3.11:6.1":"So sabbasattuttamo aggapuggalo, ","snp3.11:6.2":"Narasabho sabbapajanamuttamo; ","snp3.11:6.3":"Vattessati cakkamisivhaye vane, ","snp3.11:6.4":"Nadamva siho balava migabhibhu”. ","snp3.11:7.1":"Tam saddam sutva turitamavasari so, ","snp3.11:7.2":"Suddhodanassa tada bhavanam upavisi; ","snp3.11:7.3":"Nisajja tattha idamavocasi sakye, ","snp3.11:7.4":"“Kuhim kumaro ahamapi datthukamo”. ","snp3.11:8.1":"Tato kumaram jalitamiva suvannam, ","snp3.11:8.2":"Ukkamukheva sukusalasampahattham; ","snp3.11:8.3":"Daddallamanam siriya anomavannam, ","snp3.11:8.4":"Dassesu puttam asitavhayassa sakya. ","snp3.11:9.1":"Disva kumaram sikhimiva pajjalantam, ","snp3.11:9.2":"Tarasabhamva nabhasigamam visuddham; ","snp3.11:9.3":"Suriyam tapantam saradarivabbhamuttam, ","snp3.11:9.4":"Anandajato vipulamalattha pitim. ","snp3.11:10.1":"Anekasakhanca sahassamandalam, ","snp3.11:10.2":"Chattam maru dharayumantalikkhe; ","snp3.11:10.3":"Suvannadanda vitipatanti camara, ","snp3.11:10.4":"Na dissare camarachattagahaka. ","snp3.11:11.1":"Disva jati kanhasirivhayo isi, ","snp3.11:11.2":"Suvannanikkham viya pandukambale; ","snp3.11:11.3":"Setanca chattam dhariyanta muddhani, ","snp3.11:11.4":"Udaggacitto sumano patiggahe. ","snp3.11:12.1":"Patiggahetva pana sakyapungavam, ","snp3.11:12.2":"Jigisako lakkhanamantaparagu; ","snp3.11:12.3":"Pasannacitto giramabbhudirayi, ","snp3.11:12.4":"“Anuttarayam dvipadanamuttamo”. ","snp3.11:13.1":"Athattano gamanamanussaranto, ","snp3.11:13.2":"Akalyarupo galayati assukani; ","snp3.11:13.3":"Disvana sakya isimavocum rudantam, ","snp3.11:13.4":"“No ce kumare bhavissati antarayo”. ","snp3.11:14.1":"Disvana sakye isimavoca akalye, ","snp3.11:14.2":"“Naham kumare ahitamanussarami; ","snp3.11:14.3":"Na capimassa bhavissati antarayo, ","snp3.11:14.4":"Na orakayam adhimanasa bhavatha. ","snp3.11:15.1":"Sambodhiyaggam phusissatayam kumaro, ","snp3.11:15.2":"So dhammacakkam paramavisuddhadassi; ","snp3.11:15.3":"Vattessatayam bahujanahitanukampi, ","snp3.11:15.4":"Vittharikassa bhavissati brahmacariyam. ","snp3.11:16.1":"Mamanca ayu na ciramidhavaseso, ","snp3.11:16.2":"Athantara me bhavissati kalakiriya; ","snp3.11:16.3":"Soham na sossam asamadhurassa dhammam, ","snp3.11:16.4":"Tenamhi atto byasanangato aghavi”. ","snp3.11:17.1":"So sakiyanam vipulam janetva pitim, ","snp3.11:17.2":"Antepuramha niggama brahmacari; ","snp3.11:17.3":"So bhagineyyam sayam anukampamano, ","snp3.11:17.4":"Samadapesi asamadhurassa dhamme. ","snp3.11:18.1":"“Buddhoti ghosam yada parato sunasi, ","snp3.11:18.2":"Sambodhipatto vivarati dhammamaggam; ","snp3.11:18.3":"Gantvana tattha samayam paripucchamano, ","snp3.11:18.4":"Carassu tasmim bhagavati brahmacariyam”. ","snp3.11:19.1":"Tenanusittho hitamanena tadina, ","snp3.11:19.2":"Anagate paramavisuddhadassina; ","snp3.11:19.3":"So nalako upacitapunnasancayo, ","snp3.11:19.4":"Jinam patikkham parivasi rakkhitindriyo. ","snp3.11:20.1":"Sutvana ghosam jinavaracakkavattane, ","snp3.11:20.2":"Gantvana disva isinisabham pasanno; ","snp3.11:20.3":"Moneyyasettham munipavaram apucchi, ","snp3.11:20.4":"Samagate asitavhayassa sasaneti. ","snp3.11:20.5":"Vatthugatha nitthita. ","snp3.11:21.1":"“Annatametam vacanam, ","snp3.11:21.2":"Asitassa yathatatham; ","snp3.11:21.3":"Tam tam gotama pucchami, ","snp3.11:21.4":"Sabbadhammana paragum. ","snp3.11:22.1":"Anagariyupetassa, ","snp3.11:22.2":"Bhikkhacariyam jigisato; ","snp3.11:22.3":"Muni pabruhi me puttho, ","snp3.11:22.4":"Moneyyam uttamam padam”. ","snp3.11:23.1":"“Moneyyam te upannissam, ","snp3.11:23.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp3.11:23.3":"Dukkaram durabhisambhavam; ","snp3.11:23.4":"Handa te nam pavakkhami, ","snp3.11:23.5":"Santhambhassu dalho bhava. ","snp3.11:24.1":"Samanabhagam kubbetha, ","snp3.11:24.2":"Game akkutthavanditam; ","snp3.11:24.3":"Manopadosam rakkheyya, ","snp3.11:24.4":"Santo anunnato care. ","snp3.11:25.1":"Uccavaca niccharanti, ","snp3.11:25.2":"Daye aggisikhupama; ","snp3.11:25.3":"Nariyo munim palobhenti, ","snp3.11:25.4":"Ta su tam ma palobhayum. ","snp3.11:26.1":"Virato methuna dhamma, ","snp3.11:26.2":"Hitva kame paropare; ","snp3.11:26.3":"Aviruddho asaratto, ","snp3.11:26.4":"Panesu tasathavare. ","snp3.11:27.1":"Yatha aham tatha ete, ","snp3.11:27.2":"Yatha ete tatha aham; ","snp3.11:27.3":"Attanam upamam katva, ","snp3.11:27.4":"Na haneyya na ghataye. ","snp3.11:28.1":"Hitva icchanca lobhanca, ","snp3.11:28.2":"Yattha satto puthujjano; ","snp3.11:28.3":"Cakkhuma patipajjeyya, ","snp3.11:28.4":"Tareyya narakam imam. ","snp3.11:29.1":"Unudaro mitaharo, ","snp3.11:29.2":"Appicchassa alolupo; ","snp3.11:29.3":"Sada icchaya nicchato, ","snp3.11:29.4":"Aniccho hoti nibbuto. ","snp3.11:30.1":"Sa pindacaram caritva, ","snp3.11:30.2":"Vanantamabhiharaye; ","snp3.11:30.3":"Upatthito rukkhamulasmim, ","snp3.11:30.4":"Asanupagato muni. ","snp3.11:31.1":"Sa jhanapasuto dhiro, ","snp3.11:31.2":"Vanante ramito siya; ","snp3.11:31.3":"Jhayetha rukkhamulasmim, ","snp3.11:31.4":"Attanamabhitosayam. ","snp3.11:32.1":"Tato ratya vivasane, ","snp3.11:32.2":"Gamantamabhiharaye; ","snp3.11:32.3":"Avhanam nabhinandeyya, ","snp3.11:32.4":"Abhiharanca gamato. ","snp3.11:33.1":"Na muni gamamagamma, ","snp3.11:33.2":"Kulesu sahasa care; ","snp3.11:33.3":"Ghasesanam chinnakatho, ","snp3.11:33.4":"Na vacam payutam bhane. ","snp3.11:34.1":"Alattham yadidam sadhu, ","snp3.11:34.2":"Nalattham kusalam iti; ","snp3.11:34.3":"Ubhayeneva so tadi, ","snp3.11:34.4":"Rukkhamvupanivattati. ","snp3.11:35.1":"Sa pattapani vicaranto, ","snp3.11:35.2":"Amugo mugasammato; ","snp3.11:35.3":"Appam danam na hileyya, ","snp3.11:35.4":"Dataram navajaniya. ","snp3.11:36.1":"Uccavaca hi patipada, ","snp3.11:36.2":"Samanena pakasita; ","snp3.11:36.3":"Na param digunam yanti, ","snp3.11:36.4":"Nayidam ekagunam mutam. ","snp3.11:37.1":"Yassa ca visata natthi, ","snp3.11:37.2":"Chinnasotassa bhikkhuno; ","snp3.11:37.3":"Kiccakiccappahinassa, ","snp3.11:37.4":"Parilaho na vijjati. ","snp3.11:38.1":"Moneyyam te upannissam, ","snp3.11:38.2":"Khuradharupamo bhave; ","snp3.11:38.3":"Jivhaya talumahacca, ","snp3.11:38.4":"Udare sannato siya. ","snp3.11:39.1":"Alinacitto ca siya, ","snp3.11:39.2":"Na capi bahu cintaye; ","snp3.11:39.3":"Niramagandho asito, ","snp3.11:39.4":"Brahmacariyaparayano. ","snp3.11:40.1":"Ekasanassa sikkhetha, ","snp3.11:40.2":"Samanupasanassa ca; ","snp3.11:40.3":"Ekattam monamakkhatam, ","snp3.11:40.4":"Eko ce abhiramissasi; ","snp3.11:40.5":"Atha bhahisi dasadisa. ","snp3.11:41.1":"Sutva dhiranam nighosam, ","snp3.11:41.2":"Jhayinam kamacaginam; ","snp3.11:41.3":"Tato hirinca saddhanca, ","snp3.11:41.4":"Bhiyyo kubbetha mamako. ","snp3.11:42.1":"Tam nadihi vijanatha, ","snp3.11:42.2":"Sobbhesu padaresu ca; ","snp3.11:42.3":"Sananta yanti kusobbha, ","snp3.11:42.4":"Tunhi yanti mahodadhi. ","snp3.11:43.1":"Yadunakam tam sanati, ","snp3.11:43.2":"Yam puram santameva tam; ","snp3.11:43.3":"Addhakumbhupamo balo, ","snp3.11:43.4":"Rahado purova pandito. ","snp3.11:44.1":"Yam samano bahum bhasati, ","snp3.11:44.2":"Upetam atthasanhitam; ","snp3.11:44.3":"Janam so dhammam deseti, ","snp3.11:44.4":"Janam so bahu bhasati. ","snp3.11:45.1":"Yo ca janam samyatatto, ","snp3.11:45.2":"Janam na bahu bhasati; ","snp3.11:45.3":"Sa muni monamarahati, ","snp3.11:45.4":"Sa muni monamajjhaga”ti. ","snp3.11:45.5":"Nalakasuttam ekadasamam. "}